Amendments to the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 which update the
schedules dealing with high quality management waters, common and
scientific names of fish, stocked trout waters, close times, daily quotas
and size limits, and restrict the use of powered boats on specified bodies
of water.
